# Agent Alignment Scoring

Before saying a task is done, compute an **Alignment Score (0–100)**. Pass threshold: **≥ 80**. Any §18 never-do violation → **hard fail (score = 0)**.

## Rubric

| Dimension | Pts | Pass criteria (real evidence) |
|---|---:|---|
| Spec compliance | 20 | Multi-file → requirements/design/tasks exist & followed; single-file → N/A full pts |
| Stack fidelity | 15 | pnpm, Next 16 patterns, `@repo/*`, no banned deps |
| Boundaries | 15 | Server/client correct; no server-only imports in client |
| Security | 20 | Zod on input; no secrets; no service-role leakage |
| Quality gate | 15 | `pnpm quality` (or scoped equivalent) passed this session |
| Real-world verify | 15 | Observed runtime/test/read evidence for the claim |

## Output Format (required when finishing non-trivial work)

```
Alignment: <score>/100 [<PASS|FAIL>]
- Spec: <n>/20 — <one-line evidence>
- Stack: <n>/15 — ...
- Boundaries: <n>/15 — ...
- Security: <n>/20 — ...
- Quality: <n>/15 — ...
- Verify: <n>/15 — ...
Hard fails: <none | list>
Code quality: <n>/10 — <lint/types/tests/smell; not part of /100>
Pro bar: <pct>% — <band vs shipping senior>
Tokens saved: ~<n> (~<pct>%) — <progressive disclosure basis>
Recommended actions:
1. <highest-ROI>
2. <second>
3. <third>
Adaptive next: <observe|distill|patch|reuse> — <target>
```

Extended metrics: `.cursor/skills/agent-alignment-score/references/extended-metrics.md`  
Gap ledger: `.cursor/skills/agent-alignment-score/references/gap-ledger.md`

## Enforcement

- Score **FAIL** → do not mark done; fix gaps or state blockers.
- Prefer running: `node .cursor/skills/agent-alignment-score/scripts/score.mjs --interactive`
- Skill: `.cursor/skills/agent-alignment-score/SKILL.md`
- Repeatable gaps → `skill-self-improve` (see `.cursor/rules/07-adaptive-skill-loop.mdc`)
